    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Sketching the Moon was a great start. Gather a 50 mm magnifying lens, a 20 mm magnifying lens, a cardboard mailing tube, masking tape and a camera tripod. Inspect each lens for chips, work in a shaded area and keep the tube pointed away from the Sun. Ready?",
